column5: This crack was on the news tonight , BUT there are others starting around Long Shoal.  It's deffinettly a different year out there than years previous. Someone put there truck into a crack last week and had to be extricated out $$$$$ . As for the fishing .....  Move , move , move , and move again. Very slow for us today.
Ya, we crossed one twice yesterday.  We were surprised it was not as bad as other years, but I'm sure it will change alot in the next few days.  Play safe everyone and thanks for the info.
IMO the cracks are better than ive ever seen them this year.  Always be wary of cracks. Any lake...any time of year.  S.
No significant cracks off Willow Beach.  Fishing slow.    Nice day.  Need sunscreen
Gonna see if I can make it up there this weekend
Gonna see if I can make it up there this weekend   Catch a few for team 6!!!
